      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$33,900 - Clean, well-kept car in good condition that looks sharp, runs well, and is ready to be enjoyed. It shows the kind of light wear you\u2019d expect from a used vehicle, but overall it presents nicely inside and out and has clearly been cared for. A strong option for someone wanting a quality car without paying mint-condition money.",
